#: thunar/thunar-preferences-dialog.c:1231
msgid ""
"Indicates the behavior during multiple copies:\n"
"- Always: all copies are done simultaneously\n"
"- Local Files Only: simultaneous copies for local (not remote, not attached) "
"files\n"
"- Local Files Only (Same Devices): if all files are local but on different "
"devices (disks, mount points), copies will be sequential\n"
"- Local Files Only (Idle Devices): if all files are local but on busy "
"devices (disks, mount points), copies will be sequential\n"
"- Never: all copies are done sequentially"
msgstr ""
"Imaonetsa khalidwe zikakhalapo zambiri zofanana ndikubwerezedwa:\n"
"- Nthawi Zonse: zobwerezedwa zonse zimapangidwa nthawi imodzi\n"
"- Ma Fayilo amu Kompyuta Momwemu: zobwerezedwa zomwe zimapangidwa nthawi "
"imodzi za ma fayilo amu kompyuta momwemu (osati akutali, kapena ophatika "
"moonjezera)\n"
"- Ma Fayilo amu Kompyuta Momwemu (Zipangizo zofanana): ngati ma ma fayilo "
"ali amu kompyuta momu koma pa zipangizo zosiyana (madisiki, zoikidwa "
"pamwamba), zobwerezedwa zipangidwa motsatizana\n"
"- Ma Fayilo amu Kompyuta Momwemu (Zipangizo zongokhala): ngati ma ma fayilo "
"ali amu kompyuta momu koma pa zipangizo zotanganidwa (madisiki, zoikidwa "
"pamwamba), zobwerezedwa zipangidwa motsatizana\n"
"- Ayi Konse: zobwerezedwa zonse zipangidwa motsatizana"

#: thunar/thunar-preferences-dialog.c:1245
msgid "Local Files Only (Same Devices)"
msgstr "Ma Fayilo amu Kompyuta Momwemu (Zipangizo zofanana)"

