msgstr ""
"Gwiritsani ntchito fayilo la mwasanga la pakatipati '*.partial~' kuti "
"mukopere mafayilo. Izi zipewa mafayilo odukizana/ogawikana. Fayilo latsopano "
"liwonetsedwa pokha pokha linakoperedwa bwino bwino ndikumalidza."

#: thunar/thunar-preferences-dialog.c:1296
msgid "Verify file contents on copy:"
msgstr "Tsimikizani za mkati mwa ma fayilo pokopera:"

#: thunar/thunar-preferences-dialog.c:1300
msgid ""
"Compare contents of original file and copy in order to detect corruption. "
