"destination media, Thunar may be unable to bypass filesystem caches, so this "
"comparison may not detect all instances of corruption. Enabling this option "
"will increase copy time."
msgstr ""
"Fananizani za mkati mwa fayilo lenileni ndilokopera kuti mupeze "
"ndikuzindikira kuonongeka. Pamene izi ziyetsa kufananiza za mkati zenizeni "
"zimene zili ku malo kofikira, Thunar atha kukanika kubowoleza kosunga "
"mafayilo ena mu kompyuta, ndiye fanizo limeneli silingathe kupeza komanso "
"kuzindikira kuonongeka kwa njira zonse zimene zitha kukhalapo. Kuyatsa "
"chisankho chimenechi kuonjezera nthawi imene ingafunike kuti fayilo litha "
"kukoperedwa."

